<span id="freeTextContainer3358429458721174375">If you want to learn of the waring in the spirit for liberty and freedom as well as kingdom unity, and if you want to do so in a fun and exciting way, this Pendragon Series by Stephen Lawhead is a wonder way to do it. This is some serious soldiering herein. <br/>I enjoyed all five books and will probably read them again in a couple years...</span>

          </span>
